# RestClient (blocking) endpoints - BookController

### Get all books
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books

### Get one book by id (happy path)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/1

### Get a book that doesn't exist (expect 404 -> ProductNotFoundException)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/123456

