############################################################
# WebClient (non-blocking) endpoints - BookController
############################################################

### Get all books (async)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/async

### Get one book by id (async)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/async/1

### Get a book that doesn't exist (async)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/async/123456

# Chaos IDs: exercise the async error handling

### Chaos 991 (async)
