# Parallel fetch (Mono.zip) - two books at once

### Parallel
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/async/parallel?id1=1&id2=2

### Parallel, both slow, total should be ~5s
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/async/parallel?id1=999&id2=999

### Parallel, one fails, whole call fails
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/async/parallel?id1=1&id2=993